<doc id="551232" wikidata="Q3359355" url="?curid=551232" title="Software Park Thailand">
<text>Software Park Thailand is a government agency under the National Science and Technology Development Agency. It was established to stimulate the development of the Thai software industry. It maintains a close association with the private sector. It is in Pak Kret, Nonthaburi Province.

== Other software parks in Thailand ==
* E-saan Software Park. Khon Kaen Province
* MISOLIMA Software and Technology Park, Chiang Mai Province
* Software Park Phuket Province
* Samui Software Park. Ko Samui
* Nakhon Ratchasima Province Software Park

