==Notable cover versions==
*Later in 1967, an instrumental version by jazz guitarist Wes Montgomery became his highest-charting Hot 100 hit when it peaked at No. 44. It also reached No. 10 on the &quot;Billboard&quot; Easy Listening chart. Andy Williams also recorded the song.

